Overview
==========

lsmount is a small program for formatting the /proc/mounts output

--------------------
Dependencies
--------------------

libc
libconfig
libtinfo

--------------------
Building
--------------------

Dependencies
debhelper (>=9)
libc6-dev
libconfig-dev (>=1.4.8)
libncurses-dev
asciidoc
xmlto
gzip

--------------------
Build command
--------------------

make

--------------------
Building manpage
--------------------

make manpage

